KaraneInda: {
	PreMision0: Don't look at me like that! Do I look interesting to you or something? 'Cause I'm not!
	PreMision1: That Hakari! Why is she always one step ahead?! Huh?! Don't you dare think I said I like you or anything like that, you dummy!
