	Chat0: Don't think I'm here by choice! It's just that the code forces me to spawn near you! Stupid convenient programming!
	Chat1: Why do you keep opening my chat?! It's not like I'm the protagonist of this arc or have anything important to tell you, okay?!
	Chat2: D-don't get so close! The tsundere manual says I should back away... but it doesn't say I want to.
	Chat3: W-what are you staring at?! Stop reading my dialogue lines! We're not in some visual novel!
	Chat4: D-don't get the wrong idea! It's not like I came to your world to be with you! I was just looking for a place to go to the bathroom and this happened to be on the way!
	Seguir: I-I have no choice! D-don't think I'm doing this because I want to be with you or anything!
	DejarDeSeguir: Fine, whatever... Why does this feel so crappy if it's just a game?
	Ocupada: Don't get any ideas! I'm already with someone else... so beat it!
	Beso: Wuuah...! I love, love, love, love love you! I love you more than anything! Kiss me again! KISS ME TILL THE DAY I DIEEEE!!!
}

